show.description: Mana third wedding anniversary roje, na husband nannu insult chesi, tana mistress kosam pakkaki visiresadu. Naku em power ledu ani vallu anukunnaru—but vallu ki telidu, nene ee country lo unna richest person ki daughter ni ani. Atani motham wealth anta na valle vachindi. Ade roju, fate nannu oka powerful billionaire daggariki teesukelli na jeevitam mottam marchindi. Ippudu na daggara dabbu undi, power undi, oka kotha identity undi. Time vachindi—game ippude start avthundi!
